FastAPI Overview
FastAPI is a modern, high-performance Python web framework used to build APIs. It is designed to
be easy to use while providing very fast execution speed. FastAPI is commonly used for building
RESTful APIs and backend services.
Key features of FastAPI include automatic API documentation, data validation using Pydantic, high
performance comparable to Node.js and Go, and reduced human-induced errors in code.
FastAPI is widely adopted for building microservices, AI backends, and sc

FastAPI is widely adopted for building microservices, AI backends, and scalable web applications in
Python.
